Package com.dr.nlp.sl.executor.strategy

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExecutorStrategy<R>
    ExecutorStrategy interface part of the Strategy design pattern to execute various strategies
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileToStringStrategy
    This strategy is used to read in text files into a String
    ObjectToXMLStrategy
    converts com.dr.nlp.sl.datastructure.TextFile into XML Document
    StringToObjectStrategy
    converts String into com.dr.nlp.sl.datastructure.* Objects starting with TextFile to Paragarph(s) to Sentence(s) to SentenceItem(s) such as Word(s) and Punctuation(s)
    XMLToFileStrategy
    Output XML Document to a file output file name is stored in Config object
